OL,3,CWinchester City Council leader
OL,4,Cselected as Lib Dem mayoral candidate
OL,6,FThe leader of Winchester City Council,
OL,7,FMartin Tod, has been selected as the
OL,8,FLiberal Democrat mayoral candidate for
OL,9,FHampshire and Isle of Wight.
OL,11,FIn May 2026, voters across Hampshire
OL,12,Fand the Isle of Wight will help elect
OL,13,Fa regional mayor for the first time.
OL,15,FThe new position will oversee vital
OL,16,Fareas including transport
OL,17,Finfrastructure, skills and training,
OL,18,Fhousing, strategic planning, economic
OL,19,Fgrowth and environmental priorities.
