OL,3,CWinchester City Council leader
OL,4,Cselected as Lib Dem mayoral candidate
OL,6,FCouncillor Tod said: "Next year,
OL,7,Fvoters across Hampshire, Portsmouth,
OL,8,FSouthampton and the Isle of Wight
OL,9,Fwill, for the first time, choose a
OL,10,Fdirectly elected Mayor.
OL,12,F"This new role represents a historic
OL,13,Fshift in power ` finally bringing
OL,14,Fdecision-making on housing, transport,
OL,15,Fjobs and climate action closer to the
OL,16,Fpeople who live here.
OL,18,F"We need a Mayor who doesn't just talk
OL,19,Fabout change but has a track record of
OL,20,Fdelivering it."
