OL,4,Cselected as Lib Dem mayoral candidate
OL,6,FHe said the election for a regional
OL,7,FMayor should "not be about Westminster
OL,8,Fpersonalities.
OL,10,F"It's about who will listen to local
OL,11,Fpeople, work with councils across the
OL,12,Fregion, and get on with the job."
OL,14,FDonna Jones, the current Police and
OL,15,FCrime Commissioner for Hampshire and
OL,16,Fthe Isle of Wight, has been selected
OL,17,Fas the Conservative party's official
OL,18,Fcandidate for the Mayoral role in the
OL,19,Fregion.
